<p itemprop="description">The head of business relationship management provides strategic leadership for all business-IT relationship activities across the organisation. They establish policies and frameworks that ensure IT services consistently deliver business value and maintain strong stakeholder relationships.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide strategic leadership for business relationship management across the organisation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish organisational policies and frameworks for business-IT alignment</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead senior stakeholder relationships at executive level</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive organisational transformation and change management initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Ensure IT strategy aligns with business strategy and objectives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Represent business interests in IT governance forums</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop and manage business relationship management capabilities</li>
    </ul>
</section>

